<span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Removes the council tax referendum </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">threshold and re</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">-</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">bands properties</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 28.52pt; padding-left:7.48pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Give local authorities the power to set and retain business rates </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">whilst simultaneously offering sufficient support to mitigate regional-specific problems. </span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 28.52pt; padding-left:7.48pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Set</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">s the</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> threshold for redistribution of authority revenue </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">in pro</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">portion</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> to the </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">levels</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> of </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">local </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">deprivatio</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">n</span></li></ul><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Lifts the cap on Housing Revenue Account borrowing and encourages prudent borrowing to stimulate growth.</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 10pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Responses to